            "name": "Capturing Grab",
            "subtype": "ability",
            "text": "This ability functions as Grab, plus on a success, the mantis can choose to pull the creature adjacent to it, then makes a mandibles Strike against the creature. This extra benefit doesn't apply when the mantis maintains the Grab.",
